title: Out of It
description:
The monsters used in the music video were designed by Mortensen, who also directed the video.

Mortensen posted about his involvement in his now inactive blog, with the following post on Saturday, June 25, 2011:

[b]here there be monsters[/b]

I have made a music video with the danish artist Fallulah... and monsters
FALLULAH - Out of It (2011) from plobber.org on Vimeo.

There was a video embedded within the post, however it is now defunct.
